\cf2 \strokec2 Simultaneously, a "Picture-in-Picture" (PiP) module will dynamically display the OCR sequence. It will show the raw, heavily skewed license plate cropped from the frame. A green wireframe will draw over the four corners of the plate, and in a smooth React animation, the skewed polygon will stretch and flatten into a perfect rectangle. The final text string (e.g., KA-03-KY-1234) will type out below it, proving the effectiveness of the OpenCV warping pipeline to the technical judges.
