\f0\b\fs37\fsmilli18667 \cf2 \strokec2 High-Level Execution
\f1\fs28 \cf0 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \strokec2 The Omni-Gaze pipeline executes a sequence of advanced computer vision tasks orchestrating both deep learning models and traditional image processing.
\f3\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 YOLOv12 Inference & Tracking:
\f2\b0  The PyTorch YOLOv12 model runs inference to output bounding boxes for multiple classes. Concurrently, a tracking algorithm (such as Deep SORT or ByteTrack) assigns unique IDs to vehicles to maintain object permanence across frames
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 26
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2 .\cf0 \strokec3 \
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Relational Violation Logic:
\f2\b0  Custom Python logic determines the violation based on spatial and temporal relationships.\cf0 \strokec3 \
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Perspective Correction:
\f2\b0  For license plates, OpenCV (cv2.Canny, cv2.findContours) isolates the exact quadrilateral of the plate
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 28
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2 . The cv2.approxPolyDP function identifies the four vertices
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 28
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2 . The cv2.getPerspectiveTransform function computes the transformation matrix, and cv2.warpPerspective applies it, correcting the affine and perspective distortion
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 22
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2 .\cf0 \strokec3 \
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 TrOCR Extraction:
\f2\b0  The flattened plate crop is passed to the TrOCR processor. The vision encoder extracts features, and the sequence-to-sequence decoder predicts the final text array, successfully parsing Indian license plate formats
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 24
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2 .\cf0 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \strokec2 The specific violation classification relies on distinct geometric and temporal rulesets, ensuring robust detection across various traffic laws.
\f3\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \
